---
title: Mediterranean Whole-Roasted Cauliflower with Coriander-Spiced Chickpeas & Dilled Yogurt Sauce
description: Roasting the cauliflower crown whole allows the exterior to develop a deliciously golden brown crust. Similarly, chickpeas become crispy on the outside and creamy on the inside when oven-roasted. A generous drizzle of dilled yogurt sauce completes this Mediterranean-inspired plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/554a405c4dab71716c8b456e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/554a405c4dab71716c8b456e.pdf
